Telekom Austria Hires Merrill in Takeover Defense, WiBlatt Says

-- B y   B o r i s   G r o e n d a h l
-- 
2011-10-03T05:22:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/telekom-austria-hires-merrill-in-takeover-defense-wiblatt-says.html
Telekom Austria AG (TKA)  has hired Bank of
America Merrill Lynch to defend against a hostile takeover bid
probably led by investor Ronny Pecik, Austrian daily
WirtschaftsBlatt reported, citing an “insider.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Boris Groendahl at 
 bgroendahl@bloomberg.net  